data.text:
Madison Square Garden 3-21-84 unofficial live album Venue Madison Square Garden, New York, NY, USA Recorded 21 March 1984 Released Unknown Label Unknown Label Catalogue no. None Format 2xCD Length 12 tracks Genre Pop Producer Duran Duran Duran Duran

Madison Square Garden is an unofficial Duran Duran live album, recorded during The Sing Blue Silver Tour at Madison Square Garden in New York, NY, USA on 21 March 1984.

Track listing[]

No cat. #[]

"Hungry Like the Wolf"

"The Reflex"

"New Moon on Monday"

"Union of the Snake"

"New Religion"

"Cracks in the Pavement"

"The Seventh Stranger"

Disc 2[]

"Save A Prayer"

"Planet Earth"

"Rio"

"Girls on Film"

Personnel[]

Duran Duran are:

Simon Le Bon - vocals

John Taylor - bass guitar

Andy Taylor - guitar

Nick Rhodes - keyboards

Roger Taylor - drums

With:

Andy Hamilton - saxophone

Raphael Dejesus - percussion

B.J. Nelson - backing vocals

Charmaine Burch - backing vocals
